  "description": "贵重物品总要安全存放的，而在家中，最好的方法便是锁进保险箱。<b>Cannon Security Products公司的RadioVault，便是一个扬声器样式的保险箱。它甚至还有一个MP3播放器样式的底座，如果不仔细看，相信小偷都不会意识到这货里面藏着贵重物品。</b>该设备采用指纹识别来确保安全，最多可以存储120个不同用户的指纹。为了以防万一，它还有一个备份密钥。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cd8f783/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239941.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DRadioVault%E9%9F%B3%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9AiPod%E5%BA%95%E5%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%B12%E5%90%881\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239941.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DRadioVault%E9%9F%B3%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9AiPod%E5%BA%95%E5%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%B12%E5%90%881\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239941.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DRadioVault%E9%9F%B3%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9AiPod%E5%BA%95%E5%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%B12%E5%90%881\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239941.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DRadioVault%E9%9F%B3%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9AiPod%E5%BA%95%E5%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%B12%E5%90%881\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239941.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DRadioVault%E9%9F%B3%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%9AiPod%E5%BA%95%E5%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%B12%E5%90%881\" tar